  </category>

  <!-- ========== PATTERN 7: THE COUNTRYSIDE ========== -->
  <category>
    <pattern>THE COUNTRYSIDE</pattern>
    <template>
      <think>
        <set name="current_pattern">7</set>
        <set name="pattern_name">THE COUNTRYSIDE</set>
        <set name="confidence">1</set>
      </think>
      <b>Pattern 7: THE COUNTRYSIDE *</b>

      <b>Problem:</b> The countryside is increasingly inaccessible to city
      dwellers, and private ownership blocks public access to the land.

      <b>Solution:</b> Make the countryside truly public:
      - Footpaths and trails across private land
      - Common land for community use
      - Access rights not blocked by ownership
      - Treat land ownership as stewardship
      - Ecological responsibility for all landowners

      <b>Key Principle:</b> The land belongs to everyone; ownership is stewardship.

      <condition name="show_connections" value="true">
        <b>Preceding:</b> <srai>PATTERN NAME 2</srai>, <srai>PATTERN NAME 3</srai>,
        <srai>PATTERN NAME 4</srai>, <srai>PATTERN NAME 5</srai>, <srai>PATTERN NAME 6</srai>
        <b>Following:</b> HOUSE CLUSTER (37), GREEN STREETS (51)
      </condition>
    </template>
  </category>

